column2: b'Journey: Taiko Arabia Hantou de no Kiseki to Tatakai no Monogatari'

b'The Journey is a Japanese\xe2\x80\x93Saudi Arabian animated film co-produced by Toei Animation and Manga Productions directed by Shizuno Koubun. The film revolves around a potter named Aws who joins a battle to defend his home city.\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)'
